Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:36.63,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}配合著步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.63,0:22:42.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}時鐘停擺 淡淡的詛咒纏繞著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.59,0:22:47.05,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HB73EBC&\blur3}你的反應總是在逃避
