Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.25,0:23:25.59,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}我也仍想愛下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:28.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\t(1900,2400,\3c&HC2B44C&)}夜色滿溢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:30.76,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\3c&HC2B44C&\blur3}在這個不知餘年多少的今天
